     <div class="col274"> 
      <div class="row entry"> 
       <h2 class="row                                        brown           cat-title">Compensation</h2> 
       <div class="row promo"> 
        <div class="promo-caption">
         <p>UC offers employees a comprehensive compensation package, including competitive salaries and a full range of benefits, services and programs. Use our calculator to see the full value of your compensation. </p>
        </div> 
        <ul> 
         <li><a href="total-compensation-calculator.php">Total Compensation Calculator</a></li> 
         <li><a href="http://www.ucop.edu/academic-personnel/compensation/index.html">Academic Salaries</a></li> 
         <li><a href="http://policy.ucop.edu/doc/4010400/PPSM-30.pdf">Compensation policies for staff</a></li> 
         <li><a href="../labor/bargaining-units/index.html">Contract details for represented employees</a></li> 
         <li><a href="http://ucnet.universityofcalifornia.edu/system_series/index.html">Systemwide Series Concepts / Job Specifications</a></li> 
        </ul> 
       </div> 
      </div> 
      <div class="divider-short"></div> 
      <div class="row entry"> 
       <div class="row promo"> 
        <div class="promo-caption">
         <p>You can find more detailed information about compensation on your campus website:</p> 
         <div id="hide">
          <label for="campus-compensation" style="display: inline;">Campus Compensation websites:</label>
         </div> 
